*** CHANGES IN V2:

- Now Scopone Scientifico has a beautiful set of italian cards, thanks to
Giuseppe Mammano.

- Cards' bitmaps are loaded from an external iff file; you can draw your
personal card set.  The old (and ugly) french set is still in the archive
for those who are accustomed to play Scopone with it.

- Double-click plays card.

